title: Not patching: unknown error
body:
My game will not patch giving me an unknown error and asking to check the logs. I DL'd the hextech repair tool, ran the re-patch option. Did not work. Ran the game as administrator which started downloading the patch but then gave me the same error after downloading. Here is the LoLPatcher log:

replies.body: Are you still having issues patching?  There were issues earlier but all is well now.  Bookmark our [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page for updates on any server issues like that.  Let me know if you still have any issues!
